&lt;p&gt;Mural Health is a fast-growing clinical technology start-up that makes clinical trials easier for participants.&amp;nbsp; Our mission is to eliminate any barriers participants or caregivers experience while being part of a clinical trial. Mural Health is looking to expand our team with a Accounting Manager.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who are you? &lt;/strong&gt;We&#39;re looking for a detail-oriented and forward-thinking Accounting Manager to own our core finance operations while actively building the systems and automation infrastructure that will scale with us. This role sits at the intersection of accounting fundamentals and operational innovation — you&#39;ll keep the books clean and the close tight while continuously finding smarter, more automated ways to work. If you&#39;re the type who finishes a manual process and immediately asks &quot;how do we never do this by hand again,&quot; this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
